  "key": "C# major",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 8,
  "lyrics": "I used to be able to see all that was ahead of me. I used to look at you like maybe you knew. You told me, baby, you had the answers to it all. You told me that you, you knew, you knew. And I thought that I saw, but all I seen was imaginary. My imagination, it's taking me to places I reach. Sometimes I close my eyes, and I hope it's not true. I look at you like you knew. I look at you like you should have protected me. But I should have protected you. My heart's here for you always, always. And I thought I did it. I don't know what to do to get back to where you thought I was. They put me up on that fucking pedestal. Why are you so cold? I thought you knew. I needed you to know. I believed in you. Now I call you on the phone. I don't know what I'm doing. I'm just so angry. Sometimes I look at you minute by minute, call by call. I don't know for the first time. Maybe the second time. I don't really fucking know. All I really fucking know is that I love you. I miss you. I miss you. And I wish I could scratch you out of my mind. But you're there, you're there, you're there. Every time I close my eyes, you're there, you're there, you're there. And I wipe the tears from my eyes. I think about you all the time. I need you to be part of my life. The one that doesn't bring me down, the one that flips me up, I swear we can do it. You're my inspiration.",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 18.739999771118164,
      "text": "I used to be able to see all that was ahead of me.",
      "start": 8.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 23.600000381469727,
      "text": "I used to look at you like maybe you knew.",
      "start": 20.479999542236328
    },
    {
      "end": 28.280000686645508,
      "text": "You told me, baby, you had the answers to it all.",
      "start": 24
    },
    {
      "end": 37.13999938964844,
      "text": "You told me that you, you knew, you knew.",
      "start": 29.280000686645508
    },
    {
      "end": 44.540000915527344,
      "text": "And I thought that I saw, but all I seen was imaginary.",
      "start": 37.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 59.86000061035156,
      "text": "My imagination, it's taking me to places I reach.",
      "start": 46.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 68.69999694824219,
      "text": "Sometimes I close my eyes, and I hope it's not true.",
      "start": 61.099998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 73.73999786376953,
      "text": "I look at you like you knew.",
      "start": 68.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 82.81999969482422,
      "text": "I look at you like you should have protected me.",
      "start": 74.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 87.9800033569336,
      "text": "But I should have protected you.",
      "start": 84.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 96.77999877929688,
      "text": "My heart's here for you always, always.",
      "start": 87.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 101.26000213623047,
      "text": "And I thought I did it.",
      "start": 98.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 110.05999755859375,
      "text": "I don't know what to do to get back to where you thought I was.",
      "start": 102
    },
    {
      "end": 115.72000122070312,
      "text": "They put me up on that fucking pedestal.",
      "start": 110.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 120.45999908447266,
      "text": "Why are you so cold?",
      "start": 116.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 125.0199966430664,
      "text": "I thought you knew.",
      "start": 122.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 128.3800048828125,
      "text": "I needed you to know.",
      "start": 126.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 132.72000122070312,
      "text": "I believed in you.",
      "start": 129.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 141.3800048828125,
      "text": "Now I call you on the phone.",
      "start": 137.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 145.67999267578125,
      "text": "I don't know what I'm doing.",
      "start": 142.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 148.25999450683594,
      "text": "I'm just so angry.",
      "start": 146.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 160.33999633789062,
      "text": "Sometimes I look at you minute by minute, call by call.",
      "start": 150.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 168.3800048828125,
      "text": "I don't know for the first time.",
      "start": 164.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 173.16000366210938,
      "text": "Maybe the second time.",
      "start": 169.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 176.9600067138672,
      "text": "I don't really fucking know.",
